            "id": 6412174,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲2.63%，報47808.62點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間09日01:07，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲1224.16點（或2.63%），暫報47808.62點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.93%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.92%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li><li>今年以來：-3.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)領漲。宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)上漲7.07%；卡特彼勒(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)上漲5.89%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)上漲5.24%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲4.2%；波音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BA-US</a>)上漲3.88%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)下跌5.82%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)下跌2.89%；國際商業機器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:IBM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/IBM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">IBM-US</a>)下跌1.19%；賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)下跌0.67%；聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)下跌0.41%。</p></section></main>",
